(iv) the sale ^3[^4[the Corporation]] or to any municipal authority or any officer or other employee of ^3[^4[the Corporation]]on behalf of ^3[^4[the Corporation]], of any article in which he regularly trades or the purchase from ^3[^4[the Corporation]]or from any such authority, officer or other employee on behalf of ^3[^4[the Corporation]], of any article of a value in either case not exceeding five thousand rupees in the aggregate in any year during the period of the contract or work; or

